content: Within an hour of telling some idiot to take his tiny d*** and get off my timeline (after he called me a derogatory name) I was silenced and sent to Twitmo. But this guys tweet is still up after massive reporting. Go figure , ,https://,twitter.com/thepokerbob/st,atus/1012440890483228672, ,…

I reported him. I found enough of his threatening tweets. He should be buhbye soon. The guy is literally asking for guns to kill us. Telling us to wear red hats so we can be targets. Sickening. I have not tolerance for this talk.
I give him the very limited honor of INsta Block...
Twitmo! I love it. First heard on your TL.!  You get credit whether you came up with it or not :-)
